# Ratchet allowlist for scripts/agent_context/check.py.
#
# A CHANGED high-risk model (incremental / decode / cumulative / staged) must
# carry an explicit meta.agent contract (grain and/or invariants) — unless its
# name is listed here. Add a name only to unblock a change that genuinely
# can't wait for contract authoring; remove entries as contracts land. Same
# convention as scripts/checks/no_delete_insert.allow.
#
# One model name per line; '#' comments.
